query:
INSERT INTO inventory (
                ingredient_id,
                quantity,
                unit_id,
                confidence_level,
                expiration_date,
                location_id,
                notes
            )
            VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7)
            RETURNING
                inventory_id as "inventory_id!",
                ingredient_id as "ingredient_id!",
                quantity,
                unit_id as "unit_id!",
                confidence_level as "confidence_level: ConfidenceLevel",
                expiration_date,
                location_id as "location_id!",
                notes,
                created_at,
                updated_at
